===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|icon}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|εἰκών||likeness, image, portrait}}. Eastern Orthodox Church sense is attested from 1833. Computing sense first recorded in 1982.

